            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Many users use `<C-d>` and `<C-u>` instead of `<C-f>` and `<C-b>` to keep track of the texts. Maybe it's better to request the other half of the viewport up and down separately, instead of a whole on each side?",
